data.text:
Officeholders Report

This is a list of every country in Wikidata, with the office held by its Head of Government, and the current holder of that office.

Any errors or omissions can be corrected by adding or editing the office held by head of government (P1313) entry on the item for the country, or the officeholder (P1308) entry on the office.

This list will be refreshed daily (or you can trigger a manual update to see any changes you've made).

Compare: Heads of government report | Office held by head of government | Position held

This list is periodically updated by a bot. Manual changes to the list will be removed on the next update!
